examples.en: He stood up to the wall.
She stood back to let him in.
The house stood on a hill.
We stood up to see better.
A lamp stood on the table.
She stood with her back to me.
The men have been stood to.
He stood in a pool of light.
The wind stood at the westward.
A small boy stood champing gum.
He stood there numb with fear.
He stood out for better terms.
